My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 4

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

It's South Australia's turn as married couple, Deb and Rick, put their culinary skills to the test and declare war on the younger contestants in an Australiana themed restaurant.
